  "name": "How to get Edge working with label printing (Windows 11)",
  "body": "<h1 data-id=\"how-to-get-edge-working-with-label-printing-windows-11\">How to get Edge working with label printing (Windows 11)</h1>\n<p>This guide can remove the option of using IE and use Edge instead (works for both Windows 10/11)</p>\n<p><span>Still requires <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://galaxy.maropost.com/home/leaving?allowTrusted=1&amp;target=https%3A%2F%2Fdownload.epson-biz.com%2Fmodules%2Fpos%2Findex.php%3Fpage%3Dsingle_soft%26cid%3D6481%26scat%3D36%26pcat%3D3\">EPSON Virtual Port Assignment Tool</a></span></p>\n<p><span>and <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://galaxy.maropost.com/home/leaving?allowTrusted=1&amp;target=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.retailexpressmedia.com%2Fsupport%2Fdrivers%2Ffirstinstall.exe\">First Install</a></span></p>\n<hr></hr><ol><li>Open <strong>Settings </strong>in Windows</li><li>Type in <strong>Find a setting</strong></li><li>\n<pre class=\"code codeBlock\" spellcheck=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\"><br/><strong>Optional<br/></strong></pre>\n\t</li><li>Press <strong>Add optional feature</strong><br/><img alt=\"rtaImage - 2023-07-08T112111.971.png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppNpLEAU.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppNpLEAU.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppNpLEAU.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppNpLEAU.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppNpLEAU.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppNpLEAU.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppNpLEAU.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppNpLEAU.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></li><li>Ensure <strong>Internet Explorer Mode </strong>is enabled<br/><img alt=\"rtaImage - 2023-07-08T112116.095.png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppORCEA2.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppORCEA2.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppORCEA2.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppORCEA2.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppORCEA2.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppORCEA2.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppORCEA2.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppORCEA2.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></li><li>Open <strong>Microsoft Edge &gt; Settings &gt; Default Browser</strong><br/><img alt=\"rtaImage - 2023-07-08T112124.231.png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppORWEA2.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppORWEA2.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppORWEA2.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppORWEA2.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppORWEA2.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppORWEA2.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppORWEA2.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppORWEA2.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img><br/><br/><img alt=\"rtaImage - 2023-07-08T112132.694.png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppO0lEAE.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppO0lEAE.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppO0lEAE.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppO0lEAE.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppO0lEAE.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppO0lEAE.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppO0lEAE.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppO0lEAE.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></li><li>Set <strong>Internet Explorer compatibility </strong>to <strong>Never</strong></li><li>White-List the REX URL with <strong>Internet Explorer mode pages</strong><br/><img alt=\"rtaImage - 2023-07-08T112137.440.png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppORlEAM.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppORlEAM.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppORlEAM.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppORlEAM.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppORlEAM.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppORlEAM.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppORlEAM.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppORlEAM.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></li><li>If the <strong>Restart </strong>tab is not available / change the <strong>Allow sites to be reloaded in Internet Explorer mode </strong>to <strong>Default </strong>and back to <strong>Allow</strong><br/><br/><img alt=\"rtaImage - 2023-07-08T112142.628.png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppO4sEAE.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppO4sEAE.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppO4sEAE.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppO4sEAE.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppO4sEAE.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppO4sEAE.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppO4sEAE.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppO4sEAE.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></li><li>Open <strong>Internet Options </strong>(Type in Windows search)<br/><img alt=\"rtaImage - 2023-07-08T112147.300.png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppOTIEA2.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppOTIEA2.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppOTIEA2.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppOTIEA2.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppOTIEA2.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppOTIEA2.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppOTIEA2.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppOTIEA2.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></li><li>Adjust <strong>Active X </strong>Settings (same as Windows 10 using IE)<br/><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://galaxy.maropost.com/home/leaving?allowTrusted=1&amp;target=https%3A%2F%2Fress.zendesk.com%2Fhc%2Fen-us%2Farticles%2F203100254\">Knowledge base how to adjust Active X settings</a>\n<pre class=\"code codeBlock\" spellcheck=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\"><br/><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://galaxy.maropost.com/home/leaving?allowTrusted=1&amp;target=https%3A%2F%2Fress.zendesk.com%2Fhc%2Fen-us%2Farticles%2F203100254\">https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/203100254</a> </pre>\n\t</li><li>Now <strong>Explorer Mode </strong>websites will have a Internet Explorer logo in the URL<br/><img alt=\"rtaImage - 2023-07-08T112155.709.png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppORmEAM.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppORmEAM.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppORmEAM.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppORmEAM.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppORmEAM.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppORmEAM.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppORmEAM.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppORmEAM.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></li></ol>",
